title: how to record it in org-roam
pid: e9a09887-3d7d-4b9d-aa12-a246afc9508d
body: |2-
  At 'ideas I got from other people',
  record two subnodes:
  how it relates parent to child when used as a midparent
    if parents are of one generation or the other.
  Use that to, within each parent (in the appropriate direction)
    connect it to the child.
